Create an app on the Docker

# Create application directory!
sudo mkdir /apps/python3
cd /apps/python3

# Create Dockerfile, entrypoint.sh or copy your programs here

# Create and start = Run you container
docker run -it --rm --name my-running-script -v "$PWD":/usr/src/myapp -w /usr/src/myapp python:3 python your-daemon-or-script.py

# Detailed information:
#Please https://hub.docker.com/_/python
